    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the profession concerned with the systematic transmission of entertainment, information, advertising, and educational programming by radio or television for simultaneous reception by a scattered public audience.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
